rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c39486ddea36aae8bbb866bcdfd57986bc3749d4","tid":231194,"uid":114563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T12:43:08.000Z","msg":"player?"},{"pid":"8c734c7c7fc27b44af8358e11a813f508bc6aa20","tid":231194,"uid":43802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:54:04.000Z","msg":"今日散左，好崩潰<br />\n佢話大家嘅想法好唔同所以話想冷靜下<br />\n我就覺得其實係藉口 我覺得一段感情係可以慢慢磨合 <br />\n對我黎講冷靜下同分手冇咩分別<br />\n佢根本冇諗過要解決我同佢之間嘅問題<br />\n不過已經講咩都冇用了<br />\n佢已經唔再理我覆我機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}